Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创世之初 冥冥之中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the beginning there was darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着一声爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, bang--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生了无尽膨胀的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天 新的发现都在揭秘这个诡异\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Every day, new discoveries are unlocking the mysterious,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震撼 神秘莫测的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the mind-blowing, the deadly secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地方 - 我们所谓的《宇宙》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在《星球大战》的宇宙间 死星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the "Star Wars" universe, the Death Star
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是终极大规模杀伤性武器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is the ultimate weapon of mass destruction,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够消灭整个行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}able to annihilate entire planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在实际的宇宙间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the actual universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中充满了活生生的死亡之星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the sky is filled with real-life death stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们可以视为定时炸弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They can be thought of as sort of a time bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些是靠近我们星球的威胁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Some are dangerously close to our planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦辐射抵达我们这里 地球上的生命将可能遭遇严重的打击\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Earth's life might take a bad hit when that radiation reaches us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是地球撞上了它的枪口\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And one has the Earth in its crosshairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它让人震惊不已\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It was almost a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到时简直不敢相信\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I didn't believe it when I first saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们就是死亡之星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They are the death stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:01:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们把宇宙变成了异常险恶的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and they make the universe a very dangerous place.
