Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基于越来越多的科学证据 似乎宇宙本身\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Based on mounting scientific evidence, it appears the universe itself
