Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会把超新星推向下一步 成为伽玛射线暴\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are taking that supernova to the next step as a gamma ray burst.
