Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介于5000到8000光年之间 那是个危险区\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Being 5,000 to 8,000 light-years away, it's in the danger zone.
