Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如人们所料 你知道 它可能会有所动作的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where one would expect, well, you know, it might do something,
